<quote>當遼主疾作謀歸<pc>，</pc>有上書請避暑嵩山者<pc>，</pc>我粗人<pc>，</pc>以戰鬥取富貴<pc>，</pc>若此諛佞<pc>，</pc>未嘗為之<pc>。</pc>
</quote>
<pc>”</pc>坐中有慚者<pc>。</pc>
<date when="967">
<date notBefore="963" notAfter="968">乾德</date>
<measure quantity="5" unit="years">
<num value="5">五</num>年</measure>
</date>卒<pc>。</pc>
